---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ExpeditionCard from '../components/ExpeditionCard.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<BaseLayout title="EXPEDITION — Travel Books">
<main>
<section class="hero"><div class="container hero-grid">
<div><div class="eyebrow">Digital Travel Books</div>
<h1 class="hero-title">See less.<span>Experience more.</span></h1>
<p class="lead">Expedition není cestovní blog. Je to série digitálních knih pro lidi, kteří chtějí město projít, pochopit a skutečně si ho zapamatovat.</p>
<div class="actions"><a class="button primary" href={`${base}rome/`}>Begin Rome Expedition</a><a class="button" href={`${base}book/manifesto/`}>Read the Manifesto</a></div>
<div class="stats"><div class="stat"><strong>Volume I</strong>Rome</div><div class="stat"><strong>3 days</strong>27.–29. 8. 2026</div><div class="stat"><strong>66–74 km</strong>active journey</div><div class="stat"><strong>v0.3.0</strong>Genesis</div></div>
</div>
<div class="cover"><div class="cover-copy"><small>Volume I</small><strong>ROME</strong><span>The Eternal City</span></div><div class="cover-stamp"><b>27–29 AUGUST 2026</b><br>Filip's Expedition</div></div>
</div></section>

<section class="section alt"><div class="container">
<div class="section-heading"><div class="eyebrow">What Expedition believes</div><h2>Travel should leave you with more than photographs.</h2></div>
<div class="grid">
<ExpeditionCard number="01" title="Story before facts" text="Fakta dávají přesnost. Příběhy dávají místu význam a zůstávají v paměti." />
<ExpeditionCard number="02" title="Walk the city" text="Město se nejlépe čte v pohybu. Trasy spojují místa tak, aby společně vyprávěla jeden příběh." />
<ExpeditionCard number="03" title="Quality before quantity" text="Raději patnáct míst pochopených do hloubky než čtyřicet rychle odškrtnutých bodů." />
</div></div></section>

<section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="quote">“We do not want you to visit more places. We want every place to mean more.”</div></div></section>

<section class="section alt"><div class="container">
<div class="section-heading"><div class="eyebrow">Release roadmap</div><h2>Volume I is being built one meaningful release at a time.</h2></div>
<div class="roadmap">
<div class="roadmap-row"><strong>v0.3 Genesis</strong><span>Brand foundation, manifesto, first landing page and Rome cover.</span></div>
<div class="roadmap-row"><strong>v0.4 Empire</strong><span>Complete Day 1: Colosseum, Forum, Palatine and the first Expedition Cards.</span></div>
<div class="roadmap-row"><strong>v0.5 Vatican</strong><span>Vatican Museums, Sistine Chapel, St Peter's Basilica and baroque Rome.</span></div>
<div class="roadmap-row"><strong>v0.6 Living Rome</strong><span>Final day, viewpoints, neighbourhoods and practical expedition mode.</span></div>
<div class="roadmap-row"><strong>v1.0 Rome</strong><span>The complete first volume of the Expedition series.</span></div>
</div></div></section>
</main>
<div class="mobile-bar"><a href={base}>⌂<br>Home</a><a href={`${base}rome/`}>◉<br>Rome</a><a href={`${base}book/`}>▤<br>Book</a></div>
</BaseLayout>
